trans-unit.source: The <embeddedLabel>Delete Network Security Rule</embeddedLabel> operation deletes a network security group rule from the specified network security group.
trans-unit.target: The <embeddedLabel>Delete Network Security Rule</embeddedLabel> operation deletes a network security group rule from the specified network security group.

trans-unit.source: The <embeddedLabel>Delete Network Security Rule</embeddedLabel> request may be specified as follows.
trans-unit.target: The <embeddedLabel>Delete Network Security Rule</embeddedLabel> request may be specified as follows.

trans-unit.source: Replace <codeInline>%%amp;lt;subscription-id%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with the subscription ID and <codeInline>%%amp;lt;network-security-group-name%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with the name of the network security group, and <codeInline>%%amp;lt;rule-name%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with the name of the rule that will be deleted.
trans-unit.target: Replace <codeInline>%%amp;lt;subscription-id%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with the subscription ID and <codeInline>%%amp;lt;network-security-group-name%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with the name of the network security group, and <codeInline>%%amp;lt;rule-name%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with the name of the rule that will be deleted.
